            <div class="media-object-section middle">
                <p>
                    <strong>Expression Atlas Heatmap</strong><br>
                    You can embed the Expression Atlas heatmap as a JavaScript widget on your site. You can build it
                    from source or you can link directly to our built bundles. Instructions for both methods are
                    provided in the GitHub repository. It is strongly suggested that you go through all the examples
                    available in our showcase gallery .
                </p>
